room_title: Escape room "The Purge" by Panic Escape Room in Chicago
review: This is my second visit. This time I spent the time at the PanIQ room with my teen god-son. It was a great bonding time, the staff was welcoming, helpful and kind. Will definitely be going back!

room_title: Escape room "The Purge" by Panic Escape Room in Chicago
review: Rooms are cool, people who work there are cool and very nice. The rooms are definitely for beginners and not very difficult but they are very organized. I'd recommend checking them out if you're a beginner!
